public static ForecastStats createRandom(long minTotal, long maxTotal) {     return new ForecastStats(randomLongBetween(minTotal, maxTotal), SimpleStatsTests.createRandom(), SimpleStatsTests.createRandom(), SimpleStatsTests.createRandom(), createCountStats()). }
